  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc7 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "China's foreign exchange market plummeted in May",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "China's foreign exchange market earnings were 15.95 trillion yuan (about $ 2.38 trillion) in May, down significantly from 17.14 trillion yuan in April.",
        "In particular, the income from foreign exchange transactions between banks and their customers totaled 3.17 trillion yuan, while foreign exchange transactions between banks accounted for 12.78 trillion yuan, according to Xinhua news agency.",
        "The country's foreign exchange market revenue totaled 90.76 trillion yuan in the first five months of the year, data showed."
      ],
